      "text": "par Akminâ.Kohyn / un par pahr muins weenii Raudasch\nPuhkn.Mahjas.Weeu/un tohs\nPilsfachtus Juhda darrischu es\npohsti bes Gedshwotajeein."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kursch irr tahds gudrs\nWihrs/ kas to saproht? Un ne\nfo irr ta KUNGA Mutte run-\nnajsi? Lai wiisch to stahsta/\nRadeht irr ta Semme bohjâ gab-\njuti/ un nodeggusi ka weena\nTuknefe/ fur nerweens zaur eet?"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzij-\nja: Tadeht ka tee mannu Bauf-\nlibu irr atstahjuschi/ ko es win-\nxeem efimu preekicha lizzis/ un\nmannai Balsfnei ne irr klausij-\nschi/ nedg pehz to irr staigajfschi."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet irr staigaischi pehz\nfawas Sirds Prahta/ un teem\nBâdlim pakka/ ko winnu Teh-\nwi tohs irr mahzijfschi."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeht ta fakka tas\nKUNGS Zebaot/ tas Israêta\nDeews: Raugi / es ehdinaschu\nschobs Laudis ar Wehrmelehtm/\nun dsirdinaschu tohs ar Schul-\nta Uhdenti."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es iskaifischu tohs\nstarp teem Paganneem/ ko tee ne\nirr pasinnutchi/ nedg winnu Teh-\nwi / unn uhtischu winxeem te\nSohbinn pakka/ teekams es\nteem buhfchn Gallu darrijs."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta fakka tas KUNGS\nZebaot: Nemmeet to wehrâ/ un\nazinajeet tahs Raudu.Geeuas/\nfa tahs nahk/ un tuhtajt pehz\ntahm gudrahm (Geeuahm/)\nun laid tahs ateet."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un steidsahs / un faht"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "nu/ ka muhfas Azzis ar Al\nrahm notek/ un muhsfu Az\nPlaksteni ar Uhdentin tek."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo weena Raudaschan\nBallsne irr dsrdeta no Ziana\nAk! ka effam mehs pohstiti/me\neffam fohti Rauna likti/ jo me\neffam to Semmit atstahjusch\ntapehz ka tee muhsas Mahj\nWeetas irr avgabsuschi."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ktautajt tad ta KUNG\nWahrdn juhs Geeuas/ un la\njuhsu Anfs nskem to Wahri\nwinna Muttes/ un mahzajt ju\nfas Meitas to Raudaschanu/\nikkatra laid to ohtru Raud\nDseetmas mahza."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta Nahwe irr eeka\nputi zaur muhseem Lohgeem/\nirr muhsos jauks Nammi\nnahkuti/ tohs Behrnixus nokar\nus Eelahm/ un tohs Jauneeku\nus Gatweein."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Runna/ ta fakka ta\nKUNGS: To Zilweku nomi\nruschas Meeas gulles ka Su\ndi us Tibrunu/ un ka Ruhlini\npakka/ to Ptahweju/ ko newee\nfakrabj."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta fakka tas KUNGS\nWeens Gudrajs laid ne leclija\nsawas Gudribas pehz/ un wee\nStiprajs laid ne leeltjahs fan\nStipruma pehz/ weens Ba\ngats laid ne leclijahs faw\nBaggatibas pehz/"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet kas gribb leelitee\ntas laid leclijahs eekch ta/"
    }
  ],
